# postbackURL

**Instance Property**

A URL on your server where the testing environment sends test postbacks.

## Declaration

```swift
var postbackURL: String { get }
```

## Discussion

The testing environment sends the test postback to the [doc://com.apple.storekittest/documentation/StoreKitTest/SKAdTestPostback/postbackURL] when you call [doc://com.apple.storekittest/documentation/StoreKitTest/SKAdTestSession/flushPostbacks(responses:)].
